'''Bhagivont Gerard Majella''' zaun aslo ek Redemptorist brother. To [[Katolik firgoz|Katolik firgojecho]] ek sant zaun asa. Bhurgeank, gorban aslolea bhurgeank, avoiank ani avoiponache besar aslelea ostoreank khatir tache magnneacho adar magtat.<ref name=cssr>{{cite web|url=http://www.cssr.org.au/about_us/default.cfm?loadref=65|title=St Gerard Majella|work=cssr.org.au}}</ref>

==Jivit==
Gerard Majella [[Italy|Italiant]] Muro Lucano, Basilicata, hanga zolmololo 6 Abril 1726. Tannem zaiteo milagri kelleo:<ref name=liguori>{{cite web|url=http://mission.liguori.org/redemptorists/saints/majella/bio.htm |title=Liguori Publications:Saint Gerard Majella |work=liguori.org |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117053729/http://mission.liguori.org:80/redemptorists/saints/majella/bio.htm |archivedate=2013-01-17 |df= }}</ref>

* Ek bhurgo dongrarsavn podon melolo, taka portun jivo kelo
* Ek gorib kutumbachea gonvacher axirvad ghatlea uprant, tem gonv fudlea vorsa pasun tankam pavlem
* Zaite pavti goribank vant'talo te unde unne asounui tannem soglleank pavoxem kelem
* Ekda tannem utkacher cholon nustemkarank vadollantlean doriache ximer pavoilo

Sant Gerard Majella 16 Otubr 1755, Italiant melo.<ref name=Baltimore>{{cite web|url=http://redemptorists.net/saints-gerard.cfm |title=St. Gerard Majella, Redemptorist Saints |website=redemptorists.net |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808214147/http://redemptorists.net/saints-gerard.cfm |archivedate=2014-08-08 |df= }}</ref> Taka 29 Janer, 1893 vorsant Roma xarant Pap saib Leo XIII an bhoktivontacho mann favo kelo ani Dezembrache 11er, 1904, Pap saib sant Pius X an taka santacho mann favo kelo.<ref name="cathency">J. Magnier, 'St. Gerard Majella', Catholic Encyclopedia</ref> Saint Gerard Majellacho fest Otubrachea 16er zaun asa.

==Avoiancho patrão==
Ekdam Sant Gerardan Pirofalo familik bhett dilo ani thoisor tacho rumal soklla podlo. Tea familichea eke cheddvan jednam taka tem portun dilem, Sant Gerardan taka mhonllem "Tujem kodem dovor. Ek dis tuka hachi goroz podot".

Khup vorsanim, Gerard Majella somplea uprant, tea ostoreche bhurgem zolmotana moronk paulelem. Taka brother Gerardachim utrancho ugdas ailo ani tannem to rumal apleaxim haddunk lailo. Teach vellar, tacho dukh somplo, ani tannem borea bolaikechea bhurgeak zolm dilo. Hea ghodnnek lagon Sant Gerardak ''"il santo dei felice parti"'', mhonnge "borea zolmacho sant", mhonnon pachartat.<ref name=Tobin>{{cite web|url=http://cssr.com/english/saintsblessed/stmajella.shtml|title=Redemptorist|work=cssr.com}}</ref>

